Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:33.20,0:01:37.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,創界山是分了七層\N由神僊居住的山
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:38.23,0:01:41.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,為了打倒支配這座山的\N邪惡帝皇多惡達
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:41.94,0:01:45.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我們一邊在各界層\N與多惡達的魔神戰鬥
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:45.51,0:01:48.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,一邊以第七界層為目標進發
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:48.84,0:01:51.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,把直到第三界層的\N多惡達魔神打倒
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:51.45,0:01:53.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,令它恢復\N原來和平世界的我們
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:53.88,0:01:56.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,現在身處第四界層
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:56.75,0:01:59.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,只要把灼熱之劍\N放回胡娜拉像之上
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:59.86,0:02:02.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這個冰雪世界的第四界層
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:02.09,0:02:04.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,便能變回原來的溫暖世界了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:04.33,0:02:06.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好,我要加油!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:07.13,0:02:09.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,今天也會是又有趣又有型呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:12.54,0:02:18.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,第二十話\N龍神丸在野野神殿飛散!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:26.05,0:02:28.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這樣下去\N我便沒有立足之地了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:28.58,0:02:33.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,怎樣也要打倒渡\N平息殘兄弟的憤怒
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:39.00,0:02:40.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,怎麼了?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:45.90,0:02:48.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這個怎樣啊?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:48.80,0:02:51.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這樣護著\N胡娜拉像便萬無一失了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:55.24,0:02:57.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不要推啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:57.65,0:03:01.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,要忍耐啊\N渡,什麼事也是忍耐第一
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:06.20,0:03:07.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,喂!火美子,你坐定點啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:07.92,0:03:09.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,掉下去怎麼辦啊?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:09.40,0:03:11.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,鳥先生飛便可以了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:12.23,0:03:13.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這也是呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:14.06,0:03:16.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可是這樣比較暖呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:19.00,0:03:21.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,應該快到野野神殿了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:53.30,0:03:58.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,渡,今次一定可以收拾你\N去吧!異形軍團
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:05.30,0:04:07.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,真奇怪!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:07.42,0:04:09.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,鴨子啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:09.49,0:04:14.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,渡,這裏交給戰神丸吧\N我要決上次的勝負
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:14.12,0:04:16.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但是這裏沒有電話啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:16.63,0:04:22.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,有電話啊\N線不是斷了嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:22.73,0:04:24.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但也是電話啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:25.20,0:04:27.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,渡,快點吧\N好!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:27.54,0:04:31.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,等等,在下說交給我辦\N你還不明白嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:31.40,0:04:35.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,在下沒有事會做不到\N也不會打不通電話的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:35.41,0:04:37.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,戰-神-丸
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:37.48,0:04:41.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,戰神丸!立即趕來!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:45.49,0:04:47.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,真的來了呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:50.49,0:04:52.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,躲在西蒙後面吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:52.56,0:04:54.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,去了,戰神丸
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:04.74,0:05:05.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,雪!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:10.48,0:05:11.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這算什麼?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:21.90,0:05:24.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,戰神丸,大跳吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:37.20,0:05:38.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,大叔,很有型
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:38.84,0:05:40.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,老師,後面啊!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:41.80,0:05:43.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,糟了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:44.41,0:05:46.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,去吧!奇怪珠
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:49.82,0:05:51.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,什麼?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:53.56,0:05:58.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好,是機會了\N野牛武一郎流,交叉字斬
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:04.60,0:06:07.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,殘兄弟大人,請饒恕我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:07.37,0:06:09.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,成功了!\N師傅很強
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:09.51,0:06:11.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,河馬萬歲!河馬萬歲!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:14.60,0:06:16.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這只是小兒科
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:17.45,0:06:18.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,真不像樣呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:19.28,0:06:20.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,殘惡鳥
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:20.22,0:06:23.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,終於到我們魔界三兄弟\N展示實力的時候了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:23.79,0:06:29.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,殘酷哥哥,這世上有人\N可以戰勝我們三兄弟的嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:29.73,0:06:35.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這只是為我們勝利的歷史\N增加一個罷了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:35.33,0:06:36.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,對嗎?殘豹
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:36.63,0:06:41.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,對啊,又可以跟人說了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:41.67,0:06:46.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不只是這樣\N也可以給和我們同是四天王
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:46.71,0:06:53.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,在多惡達身邊獻慇勤的\N東哥羅一個下馬威的機會
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:53.62,0:06:55.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這不要忘記
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:58.65,0:07:01.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,雪!雪!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:03.09,0:07:06.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我沒事,渡,你看這個
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:08.03,0:07:10.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,很可愛!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:10.20,0:07:13.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,因為飛彈的爆炸炸開了雪\N我才見到的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:14.10,0:07:17.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是嗎?原來雪你從這爆炸中\N保護了這幼苗嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:18.41,0:07:20.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,雪好偉大!\N真的呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:20.64,0:07:24.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,在這麼嚴寒的地方\N竟也可生長真是頑強呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:24.38,0:07:28.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,對呢,就算第四界層\N變成了極寒地獄
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:28.85,0:07:32.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,在雪底下也有生命\N努力求生存呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:32.22,0:07:35.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我們也要加油呢,渡!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:48.64,0:07:50.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,千人僊人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:50.51,0:07:54.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,渡,你回來了嗎?\N灼熱之劍怎樣?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:54.61,0:07:57.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,正如你看見的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:57.41,0:08:00.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,各位觀眾,我來說明一下吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:00.95,0:08:06.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你們已知道了多惡達\N支配的創界山是有七層了吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:06.56,0:08:10.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,渡現在身處的第四界層
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:10.26,0:08:12.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是有座拿著\N灼熱之劍的胡娜拉像
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:12.49,0:08:16.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,而第三界層便有\N拿著極寒之劍的亞撒姆像
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:16.23,0:08:18.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,因為多把這兩把劍\N交換了的關係
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:18.83,0:08:22.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,令這兩個界層變得奇怪起來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:22.20,0:08:27.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,到底渡能否把灼熱之劍\N放回胡娜拉像身上呢?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:42.92,0:08:44.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,危險!回來啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:50.73,0:08:52.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,等你很久了,小鬼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:52.80,0:08:55.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,什麼?你們是…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:55.60,0:08:59.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我們是多惡達大人\N手下的四天王其中三人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:00.61,0:09:02.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,魔界殘兄弟
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:02.88,0:09:06.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,竟要我們出手\N你也幹得有點兒不錯呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:06.05,0:09:08.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但只是有點兒中的有點兒啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:08.45,0:09:10.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,被你們稱讚\N我一點也不高興呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:10.89,0:09:13.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這種口氣也只有到此為止了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:14.09,0:09:16.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我不會讓你\N把灼熱之劍放回去的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:16.29,0:09:18.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,能阻止我便阻止我試試吧\N來吧!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:42.05,0:09:44.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,一點用也沒有,受死吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:50.59,0:09:52.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,渡,沒事嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:52.86,0:09:54.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,雪,西蒙,謝謝你們
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:03.87,0:10:06.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好了!你怎麼辦?渡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:06.11,0:10:08.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我也可以啊,師傅,古拿瑪
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:10.75,0:10:13.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,龍神丸!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:13.02,0:10:14.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,戰神丸!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:14.95,0:10:17.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,空神丸!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:40.10,0:11:41.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,受死吧!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:43.10,0:11:45.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,野牛武一郎流,交叉字斬
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:47.91,0:11:49.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,什…什麼?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:53.18,0:11:56.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,簡單,簡單\N二哥,是時候了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:57.62,0:11:58.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,真卑鄙!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:03.96,0:12:07.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,戰神丸!振作點!\N起來,站起來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:07.40,0:12:08.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,師傅!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:09.93,0:12:11.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,讓我殺了你吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:14.24,0:12:16.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,渡,合體吧!\N古拿瑪
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:16.76,0:12:17.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:22.81,0:12:26.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,小兒科,豹,惡鳥\N合體變成合體達吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:42.56,0:12:43.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,很…很巨型
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:43.90,0:12:47.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不是大便有用的\N說得對,渡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:47.60,0:12:52.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好,去吧,天空龍牙拳!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:57.68,0:13:00.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,龍牙拳沒有效,可惡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:05.15,0:13:06.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,要打中!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:14.66,0:13:17.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可惡,不能動,渡!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:22.77,0:13:25.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,怎麼了?渡\N到此為止了嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:26.10,0:13:29.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,還沒,炎龍拳!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:31.61,0:13:33.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,龍雷拳!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:37.95,0:13:39.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,今次到我了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:43.22,0:13:44.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:44.36,0:13:46.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,飛龍拳!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:54.20,0:13:55.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,必殺!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:57.20,0:13:59.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,登龍劍!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:08.10,0:14:09.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,他接住了登龍劍
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:11.52,0:14:15.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,登龍劍,破解!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:15.09,0:14:16.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,啊!登龍劍啊!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:18.79,0:14:21.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你的死期終於到了,渡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:29.60,0:14:33.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,渡!奮鬥!\N你輸了,渡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:33.38,0:14:36.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好好睡在冰雪下吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:38.58,0:14:39.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我會輸嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:39.88,0:14:43.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,為了在冰冷的雪下\N支配著的草苗還有其他生物
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:43.05,0:14:47.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我是不可以輸的\N我一定會令這個世界復原的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:47.72,0:14:51.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,說得好\N那麼我也要戰鬥到底!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:59.50,0:15:02.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,去吧!渡,這是火炎登龍劍
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:05.07,0:15:06.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,什…什麼?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:09.71,0:15:15.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好,去吧,火炎登龍劍
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:43.98,0:15:44.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,龍神丸
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:45.28,0:15:50.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你不用理我\N快點把灼熱之劍放回去吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:51.15,0:15:52.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,明白了,我去了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:57.83,0:15:58.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,龍神丸
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:59.36,0:16:04.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不要回來\N快把灼熱之劍…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:06.30,0:16:07.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,龍神丸…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:07.80,0:16:09.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,去啊,渡!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:09.77,0:16:11.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我…我知道了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:24.60,0:16:28.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,渡,只差一步真是可惜呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:29.06,0:16:30.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可惡!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:31.99,0:16:33.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,沒用的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:34.96,0:16:37.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你慢慢地長睡吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:38.33,0:16:39.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,什麼?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:42.34,0:16:43.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,雪!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:43.94,0:16:47.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,灼熱之劍,請你救渡!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:23.08,0:17:28.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,混帳,你記著啊,渡\N不會就這樣算數的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:37.79,0:17:41.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,怎…怎麼回事?\N我不知道
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:42.80,0:17:46.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,胡娜拉和亞撒姆救了你們
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:46.03,0:17:49.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好了,快把灼熱之劍放回去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:50.20,0:17:51.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:53.90,0:17:55.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,雪…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:28.10,0:18:31.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,終於連第四界層的彩虹\N也恢復原狀了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:31.80,0:18:35.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,做得好\N一定是很辛苦的旅程了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:41.16,0:18:43.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,龍神丸,沒事吧?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:44.50,0:18:47.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,像平時提起精神啊,龍神丸
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:47.93,0:18:52.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,渡,最後的時刻到了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:52.27,0:18:53.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,最後的時刻?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:54.10,0:18:57.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我再去叫火龍把力量傳給你吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:57.87,0:19:01.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這樣你便可以復原了吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:01.50,0:19:03.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我的生命已燃燒盡了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:03.94,0:19:06.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,龍神丸…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:06.60,0:19:12.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這是騙人的\N因為還剩下三個界層啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:12.60,0:19:17.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不能…不能一起去\N我不要…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:19.06,0:19:22.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不要哭,渡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:22.60,0:19:28.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你有很多同伴,合力戰鬥吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:31.61,0:19:34.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,永別了,渡!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:36.84,0:19:40.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,龍神丸…龍神丸!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:50.10,0:19:52.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,龍神丸變成一個球了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:52.89,0:19:56.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,什麼?\N龍神丸死了嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:56.90,0:20:01.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,怎會這樣的,今後怎麼辦?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:01.50,0:20:03.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,竟會發生這種事…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:08.60,0:20:12.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,龍神丸…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:12.49,0:20:14.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,龍神丸!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:17.69,0:20:21.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,渡! 渡!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:26.40,0:20:30.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,渡,你把灼熱之劍還回來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:30.20,0:20:35.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,很多謝你\N花朵和動物們也很高興
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:35.37,0:20:36.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,胡娜拉…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:37.04,0:20:39.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,為了答謝你\N告訴你一個好消息
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:40.17,0:20:44.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,在第五界層聽說有復活聖水
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:45.01,0:20:46.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,復活聖水?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:46.50,0:20:49.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,為了正義而犧牲了性命的人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:49.38,0:20:53.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,傳說可以利用聖水\N從死者之國回來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:55.16,0:20:59.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你帶變成了龍之王的龍神丸\N上第五界層吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:00.39,0:21:02.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,要到第五界層的哪處?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:02.63,0:21:05.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,去找西裏露森林吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:08.80,0:21:11.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,西裏露森林…\N謝謝你,胡娜拉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:12.04,0:21:13.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,太好了,渡!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:14.61,0:21:19.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我要上第五界層\N我祈求能找到復活聖水
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:19.91,0:21:20.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,謝謝你!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:21.02,0:21:24.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,渡,你拿勇者之劍出來吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:25.12,0:21:26.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,勇者之劍?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:35.83,0:21:37.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這是…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:37.60,0:21:42.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我把勇者之劍加入了\N極寒之劍和灼熱之劍的力量
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:42.94,0:21:46.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,增強了成為王者之劍
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:46.84,0:21:48.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,王者之劍
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:48.28,0:21:49.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,一直戰鬥到這裏的你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:49.98,0:21:53.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,一定可以好好運用的\N你拿去吧

